        <h2 class="cag-h2">How Do We Ship a Congo African Grey Nationwide, and What Does It Cost?</h2>
        <p>We ship Congos nationwide on two honest tiers — $185 to your nearest airport or $350 to your door — and if you're within 2–3 hours of Midland, we'll steer you to a gentle local pickup instead. Every bird travels on IATA live-animal cargo with its full document folder, and we confirm the carrier and window with you before it ever leaves.</p>
