        <h3 class="cag-h3">What Are the Delivery Options and Prices?</h3>
        <p>You choose the tier that fits: airport pickup on Delta, United or American is $185, and climate-controlled home delivery is $350. Both leave with the health certificate and paperwork in hand, so arrival day is about settling your bird in, not chasing documents.</p>
