        <h4 class="cag-h4">Can You Pick Up a Congo in Person Instead of Shipping?</h4>
        <p>Yes — local pickup at our Midland, TX aviary is the gentlest handoff a bird can get, and it's open to anyone within a 2–3 hour drive. Meeting your Congo in person also lets you do the final in-real-life verification this whole page is built around.</p>
