        <p>Real families across the country now share their homes with a documented C.A.Gs Congo, and two of them say it better than we could — both bought sight-unseen, and both had the shipping and paperwork go exactly as this page promises. Dozens more accounts, with photos, live on our <a href="/african-grey-reviews/">African Grey reviews</a> page.</p>
